1
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,770
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,770 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 34=

3
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,791
(Shen Bingfan.)

4
00:00:59,458 --> 00:01:00,291
(Northern Bureau)
The day after tomorrow,

5
00:01:00,291 --> 00:01:01,125
(Northern Bureau)
His Majesty will host a garden party

6
00:01:01,125 --> 00:01:02,208
His Majesty will host a garden party

7
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:04,000
in the Imperial Garden.

8
00:01:04,458 --> 00:01:05,541
Imperial relatives,

9
00:01:06,041 --> 00:01:06,875
princes, nobles, and ministers,

10
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:08,791
along with

11
00:01:09,083 --> 00:01:10,041
the ladies of their households,

12
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,416
have all been invited.

13
00:01:11,708 --> 00:01:12,250
At midnight,

14
00:01:12,625 --> 00:01:14,125
His Majesty

15
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:15,458
will lead the officials

16
00:01:15,875 --> 00:01:17,333
up to Duanhua Gate

17
00:01:17,625 --> 00:01:18,708
to celebrate with the people.

18
00:01:20,125 --> 00:01:20,875
Therefore,

19
00:01:21,208 --> 00:01:21,708
the Cabinet

20
00:01:22,166 --> 00:01:23,125
has ordered

21
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:24,500
all men from both

22
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,833
the Southern and Northern Bureaus

23
00:01:26,125 --> 00:01:28,458
to guard His Majesty
at the Imperial Garden.

24
00:01:30,041 --> 00:01:30,666
Yes, my lord.

25
00:01:32,333 --> 00:01:33,500
But the Northern Bureau

26
00:01:34,125 --> 00:01:36,000
cannot be left completely unguarded.

27
00:01:38,041 --> 00:01:39,750
The female Jinyiwei will stay
and guard the Bureau.

28
00:01:40,333 --> 00:01:41,916
Good. In that case,

29
00:01:42,458 --> 00:01:44,291
since Hua Mange is injured,

30
00:01:44,458 --> 00:01:46,541
I will leave Duoyu here with you

31
00:01:46,833 --> 00:01:48,166
in case you are short-handed.

32
00:01:50,375 --> 00:01:50,750
Bingfan.

33
00:01:51,375 --> 00:01:53,125
Why not focus on the files tonight?

34
00:01:53,541 --> 00:01:55,458
I can patrol the front
and rear courtyards.

35
00:01:56,833 --> 00:01:57,666
After midnight,

36
00:01:57,875 --> 00:01:58,875
Duoyu will relieve you.

37
00:02:03,833 --> 00:02:04,833
Bingfan, look.

38
00:02:10,541 --> 00:02:12,083
Young Master Chang really is handsome.

39
00:02:22,333 --> 00:02:22,791
You look good.

40
00:02:24,583 --> 00:02:25,375
I haven't worn this in a long time.

41
00:02:25,458 --> 00:02:26,416
It feels a little strange.

42
00:02:37,708 --> 00:02:38,250
Don't miss me too much.

43
00:02:38,416 --> 00:02:39,083
Wait for me.

44
00:02:40,666 --> 00:02:41,916
Young Master, it's time.

45
00:02:55,458 --> 00:02:55,916
Bingfan.

46
00:02:56,625 --> 00:02:57,416
The front gate is locked.

47
00:02:58,541 --> 00:02:59,541
I locked the back gate too.

48
00:03:00,416 --> 00:03:01,708
Go to the Archives.

49
00:03:02,125 --> 00:03:03,500
I can stand watch here alone.

50
00:03:03,833 --> 00:03:04,250
All right.

51
00:03:04,875 --> 00:03:06,958
If anything happens,
fire a signal arrow.

52
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,958
I have never seen the Bureau

53
00:03:17,958 --> 00:03:19,708
(Northern Bureau)
I have never seen the Bureau

54
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:20,750
(Northern Bureau)
this quiet at this hour.

55
00:03:21,458 --> 00:03:24,291
If anyone chose this moment to attack,

56
00:03:24,583 --> 00:03:26,583
they would have the perfect opening.

57
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:31,470
(Northern Bureau)

58
00:03:38,541 --> 00:03:41,041
Hua, why are we back
at Young Master Chang's?

59
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:44,458
He has more on Leng Xin than anyone.

60
00:03:44,458 --> 00:03:46,541
We always hold our meetings here anyway.

61
00:03:49,458 --> 00:03:50,125
Duoyu.

62
00:03:50,625 --> 00:03:52,833
Something just occurred to me.

63
00:03:54,083 --> 00:03:54,500
What?

64
00:03:55,458 --> 00:03:57,458
Every witness says

65
00:03:58,375 --> 00:04:00,250
Leng Xin is small,

66
00:04:00,791 --> 00:04:02,041
fast, and agile.

67
00:04:02,625 --> 00:04:03,791
I have fought them.

68
00:04:04,875 --> 00:04:06,208
I have tracked them.

69
00:04:07,166 --> 00:04:08,791
But something always felt off.

70
00:04:09,375 --> 00:04:10,000
Off how?

71
00:04:10,875 --> 00:04:12,375
That night at Mr. Ding's house,

72
00:04:13,416 --> 00:04:15,416
they forced me back and went straight
for the kill.

73
00:04:15,708 --> 00:04:17,125
When our eyes met,

74
00:04:17,708 --> 00:04:18,833
the look in his eyes

75
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,500
was strange.

76
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:22,750
I think...

77
00:04:25,125 --> 00:04:26,250
Len Xin didn't feel like a man.

78
00:04:42,833 --> 00:04:43,291
Who's there?

79
00:04:51,041 --> 00:04:51,416
Who is it?

80
00:04:54,083 --> 00:04:55,041
Xintian.

81
00:04:58,666 --> 00:04:59,583
Taozi. It's you.

82
00:05:03,875 --> 00:05:04,750
What are you doing here so late?

83
00:05:06,458 --> 00:05:07,541
I brought you food.

84
00:05:18,541 --> 00:05:19,083
Taozi.

85
00:05:19,958 --> 00:05:21,500
I shouldn't have snapped at you before.

86
00:05:22,250 --> 00:05:23,083
I'm sorry.

87
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,208
Forgive me, all right?

88
00:05:26,125 --> 00:05:27,208
It is all right, Xintian.

89
00:05:27,875 --> 00:05:29,000
I made your favorite.

90
00:05:29,916 --> 00:05:31,041
And I brought fruit too.

91
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,291
Taozi.

92
00:05:44,125 --> 00:05:46,041
Both gates are locked.

93
00:05:46,458 --> 00:05:47,333
How did you get in?

94
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:03,250
Xintian.

95
00:06:16,375 --> 00:06:16,791
Xintian.

96
00:06:34,375 --> 00:06:37,166
(I will be waiting in the Archives.)

97
00:06:52,958 --> 00:06:54,041
Taozi?

98
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,375
What are you doing?

99
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:57,125
Untie me!

100
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,250
I told you to come with me.
You would not listen.

101
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,000
This is all your fault.

102
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:03,208
What nonsense are you talking?

103
00:07:03,208 --> 00:07:04,000
Untie me!

104
00:07:04,875 --> 00:07:05,500
Let me go!

105
00:07:06,333 --> 00:07:07,041
Xintian.

106
00:07:07,791 --> 00:07:09,375
I know you truly cared about me.

107
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:12,708
I truly wanted to put down my blade
for you.

108
00:07:18,666 --> 00:07:20,500
So why wouldn't you listen?

109
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:21,916
Why wouldn't you come with me?

110
00:07:22,291 --> 00:07:23,458
Why?

111
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,625
You are insane.

112
00:07:28,125 --> 00:07:29,208
Who are you?

113
00:07:30,291 --> 00:07:31,125
Who am I?

114
00:07:31,875 --> 00:07:33,875
You have been hunting me all along.

115
00:07:34,625 --> 00:07:34,958
You...

116
00:07:37,833 --> 00:07:39,041
You are Leng Xin?

117
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:40,041
Yes.

118
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:42,958
I'm the Bounty List's

119
00:07:43,083 --> 00:07:45,458
number-one killer,

120
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,750
Leng Xin.

121
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,541
No.

122
00:08:01,958 --> 00:08:04,416
Impossible, Taozi. Stop this.

123
00:08:04,458 --> 00:08:05,791
Untie me.

124
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:09,541
You never imagined

125
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:12,291
the person you were hunting

126
00:08:12,791 --> 00:08:14,250
was right beside you.

127
00:08:17,625 --> 00:08:20,750
You tried so hard to protect her.

128
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:23,958
You even bled and died for her.

129
00:08:28,875 --> 00:08:30,500
I don't believe this.

130
00:08:31,458 --> 00:08:32,666
How could you be Leng Xin?

131
00:08:32,708 --> 00:08:35,041
Who said Leng Xin had to be a man?

132
00:08:40,333 --> 00:08:41,500
You are Leng Xin.

133
00:08:47,416 --> 00:08:48,125
What do you want?

134
00:08:48,125 --> 00:08:48,791
Let me go!

135
00:08:48,833 --> 00:08:49,833
Let me go!

136
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,541
Soon, your dear sisters

137
00:08:54,375 --> 00:08:55,500
will come running to save you.

138
00:08:55,833 --> 00:08:56,625
Tonight,

139
00:08:58,041 --> 00:08:59,666
the Northern Bureau is empty.

140
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:02,708
It belongs to us.

141
00:09:04,208 --> 00:09:05,083
So the few of us

142
00:09:05,708 --> 00:09:07,375
can have a nice long talk.

143
00:09:09,166 --> 00:09:09,750
Bingfan.

144
00:09:10,541 --> 00:09:11,208
Bingfan.

145
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,208
Bingfan, stay away!

146
00:09:13,208 --> 00:09:15,000
Bingfan! Bingfan!

147
00:09:15,416 --> 00:09:15,791
Bingfan...

148
00:09:18,541 --> 00:09:20,125
Eliminate the impossible,

149
00:09:20,458 --> 00:09:21,416
and whatever remains,

150
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:22,875
however unbelievable,

151
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:25,458
must be the truth.

152
00:09:25,791 --> 00:09:26,333
No wonder.

153
00:09:27,791 --> 00:09:29,333
That day, we searched Meizhen House

154
00:09:29,375 --> 00:09:30,208
from top to bottom and found nothing.

155
00:09:30,666 --> 00:09:32,708
Was she hiding among the girls?

156
00:09:34,916 --> 00:09:35,291
Oh no.

157
00:09:35,583 --> 00:09:36,500
If that is true,

158
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:38,166
Leng Xin has been beside us all along.

159
00:09:38,958 --> 00:09:39,458
You mean...

160
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:40,500
Taozi?

161
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,833
It is only a guess.

162
00:09:42,375 --> 00:09:43,458
She kept clinging to Xintian

163
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:45,000
and refused to leave.

164
00:09:45,375 --> 00:09:47,500
For a weak, frightened girl

165
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:49,750
who grew up living in fear,

166
00:09:50,416 --> 00:09:51,083
that makes no sense.

167
00:09:51,416 --> 00:09:52,458
During the battle outside the capital,

168
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,083
she was in the middle of the chaos

169
00:09:54,208 --> 00:09:55,166
and escaped without a scratch.

170
00:09:55,583 --> 00:09:55,833
And

171
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,208
Guan Yunfeng died protecting her

172
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,416
when Du Bin struck.

173
00:09:59,708 --> 00:10:00,958
Maybe Guan Yunfeng

174
00:10:02,333 --> 00:10:04,375
was not killed by Du Bin at all.

175
00:10:04,708 --> 00:10:04,958
Right.

176
00:10:05,833 --> 00:10:07,875
I just got Guan Yunfeng's
autopsy report.

177
00:10:08,916 --> 00:10:09,958
Why didn't you show me earlier?

178
00:10:10,375 --> 00:10:11,625
I was in a hurry and forgot.

179
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:15,180
(Autopsy Report)

180
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,625
Just as I thought.

181
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,333
How is that possible?

182
00:10:24,333 --> 00:10:24,916
It says

183
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,166
that before Du Bin stabbed him,

184
00:10:27,833 --> 00:10:28,875
Guan Yunfeng's meridians

185
00:10:29,250 --> 00:10:30,083
had already been shattered
by internal force.

186
00:10:30,375 --> 00:10:31,875
Then we were right.

187
00:10:33,625 --> 00:10:34,291
The demon

188
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:38,041
has been with us all along.

189
00:10:51,708 --> 00:10:52,250
Xintian.

190
00:11:00,375 --> 00:11:01,291
Who did this to you?

191
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,250
Bingfan, run!

192
00:11:24,791 --> 00:11:25,791
You are Leng Xin?

193
00:11:27,291 --> 00:11:28,000
Yes.

194
00:11:31,166 --> 00:11:32,041
Are you really Leng Xin?

195
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:33,666
You don't believe me?

196
00:11:34,666 --> 00:11:36,208
Then surely you recognize
the Green Bamboo Sword.

197
00:11:43,041 --> 00:11:43,541
Why?

198
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:51,333
It is your fault! All your fault!

199
00:11:53,583 --> 00:11:54,541
I have killed so many people,

200
00:11:54,916 --> 00:11:55,416
but you,

201
00:11:55,958 --> 00:11:57,750
only you, wouldn't let me go!

202
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,500
You forced me to hide like a rat,

203
00:11:59,833 --> 00:12:01,166
and you still ask me why?

204
00:12:02,708 --> 00:12:03,375
You are the criminal.

205
00:12:03,791 --> 00:12:04,416
I'm a Jinyiwei.

206
00:12:04,708 --> 00:12:06,166
Of course I would hunt you down.

207
00:12:12,208 --> 00:12:13,041
Hunt me down?

208
00:12:13,958 --> 00:12:15,375
I was right beside you.

209
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,458
I danced circles around you.

210
00:12:17,875 --> 00:12:19,250
Yet you protected me.

211
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,625
You even bled and died for me.

212
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,333
And you think you caught me?

213
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,500
Who gave you the right?

214
00:12:24,916 --> 00:12:25,791
Who!

215
00:12:26,250 --> 00:12:27,208
Who gave you the right?

216
00:12:28,625 --> 00:12:29,750
You demon.

217
00:12:31,041 --> 00:12:32,166
Have you ever seen a demon?

218
00:12:34,458 --> 00:12:35,250
I have.

219
00:12:37,625 --> 00:12:39,916
How do you think I became this?

220
00:12:40,958 --> 00:12:43,500
I used to be an ordinary girl,
just like you.

221
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:46,541
Who turned me into this?

222
00:12:46,958 --> 00:12:48,500
What gives you the right
to call me a demon?

223
00:12:48,708 --> 00:12:49,666
What gives you the right?

224
00:12:50,625 --> 00:12:51,333
And you!

225
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,750
You!

226
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,750
You were the kindest to me.

227
00:12:55,208 --> 00:12:57,291
I even thought I could stay
as Taozi forever.

228
00:12:57,833 --> 00:12:59,500
I thought we could wander
the world together.

229
00:12:59,875 --> 00:13:01,625
But you would not stop chasing me.

230
00:13:01,958 --> 00:13:03,083
Why did you take her away?

231
00:13:03,458 --> 00:13:05,750
Why did you steal her from me?

232
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,083
Why? Why?

233
00:13:07,458 --> 00:13:09,125
Why?

234
00:13:09,833 --> 00:13:10,750
Here is the truth.

235
00:13:11,333 --> 00:13:13,083
No one ordered me to kill you today.

236
00:13:13,416 --> 00:13:14,958
This order came from me.

237
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:20,208
For the first time in my life,
I gave myself an order.

238
00:13:22,458 --> 00:13:23,125
What are you going to do?

239
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:26,458
I'm going to kill you.

240
00:13:27,458 --> 00:13:28,750
Then, burn this place to the ground.

241
00:13:29,708 --> 00:13:30,541
After tonight,

242
00:13:31,125 --> 00:13:33,000
who will know who Leng Xin was?

243
00:13:34,125 --> 00:13:36,250
Who will know who Taozi was?

244
00:13:37,625 --> 00:13:39,625
Leng Xin, all alone,

245
00:13:39,625 --> 00:13:41,375
burns the Northern Bureau to ashes.

246
00:13:41,916 --> 00:13:43,291
When my master hears of it,

247
00:13:43,875 --> 00:13:45,666
he will be proud of me.

248
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:50,083
You are mad.

249
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,791
Wait!

250
00:14:11,458 --> 00:14:12,166
You are afraid.

251
00:14:12,791 --> 00:14:13,708
I'm dead either way.

252
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,750
At least let me die knowing the truth.

253
00:14:17,875 --> 00:14:19,291
You are stalling.

254
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,083
Today is the Ghost Festival.

255
00:14:21,375 --> 00:14:22,375
Everyone in the Northern Bureau

256
00:14:23,125 --> 00:14:24,750
is guarding the Emperor
in the Imperial Garden.

257
00:14:25,958 --> 00:14:27,458
No one will know what happened here.

258
00:14:28,458 --> 00:14:30,625
Answer me first. You can kill me after.

259
00:14:33,833 --> 00:14:34,958
Or are you the one who's afraid?

260
00:14:37,166 --> 00:14:37,750
Fine.

261
00:14:38,375 --> 00:14:39,583
For Xintian's sake,

262
00:14:40,875 --> 00:14:41,458
ask.

263
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:42,458
Ask!

264
00:14:42,458 --> 00:14:43,333
Ask me!

265
00:14:47,166 --> 00:14:48,416
Were you hiding in Meizhen House?

266
00:14:51,583 --> 00:14:55,291
Who would ever think
the dreaded Leng Xin

267
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:58,083
was hiding in that filthy den?

268
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:00,125
There was food and drink,

269
00:15:00,375 --> 00:15:02,458
and I could hear every whisper at court.

270
00:15:03,333 --> 00:15:05,583
Then why didn't you act
when Meizhen House fell?

271
00:15:05,916 --> 00:15:07,083
Why would I?

272
00:15:07,791 --> 00:15:09,125
My master had just ordered me

273
00:15:09,583 --> 00:15:12,083
to remove Meizhen House,
that thorn in his side.

274
00:15:14,083 --> 00:15:16,583
Before I even had the chance
to start killing,

275
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,208
you did it for me.

276
00:15:20,333 --> 00:15:21,000
Honestly,

277
00:15:21,541 --> 00:15:23,458
I should thank you.

278
00:15:32,083 --> 00:15:32,750
Xintian.

279
00:15:33,958 --> 00:15:34,666
Scared?

280
00:15:36,375 --> 00:15:36,916
You are scared?

281
00:15:42,416 --> 00:15:43,541
Do you serve the Crown Prince?

282
00:15:44,708 --> 00:15:46,208
You are not worthy to know
my master's name.

283
00:15:46,458 --> 00:15:47,791
Ask about him again,

284
00:15:47,791 --> 00:15:48,708
and I will kill you!

285
00:16:01,791 --> 00:16:02,250
Hua.

286
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,833
The back door was bolted
from the inside. I didn't dare go in.

287
00:16:07,375 --> 00:16:08,291
You never came to relieve me.

288
00:16:09,291 --> 00:16:10,125
Then the door was locked.

289
00:16:10,833 --> 00:16:12,750
I knew something had happened.

290
00:16:13,458 --> 00:16:14,125
Then we fight our way in.

291
00:16:15,083 --> 00:16:15,416
Wait.

292
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:23,250
If that really is Leng Xin inside,

293
00:16:24,458 --> 00:16:25,458
we are no match for her.

294
00:16:26,916 --> 00:16:27,416
And

295
00:16:27,916 --> 00:16:29,458
we still don't know for certain

296
00:16:30,458 --> 00:16:31,583
whether she is Leng Xin or not.

297
00:16:33,208 --> 00:16:34,583
But Bingfan and Xintian are in danger.

298
00:16:37,291 --> 00:16:37,750
Here is what we do.

299
00:16:38,166 --> 00:16:39,083
I will check Xintian's room

300
00:16:39,625 --> 00:16:40,833
for any clues.

301
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:41,833
You go to the imperial city

302
00:16:42,458 --> 00:16:43,791
and warn Chang Beiming.

303
00:16:44,166 --> 00:16:44,583
All right.

304
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:47,583
(Northern Bureau)

305
00:16:47,583 --> 00:16:48,416
Duoyu!

306
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:52,625
Be careful.

307
00:16:53,916 --> 00:16:54,291
Don't worry.

308
00:16:55,083 --> 00:16:55,541
You too.

309
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:04,970
(Northern Bureau)

310
00:17:06,291 --> 00:17:07,500
What else do you want to ask?

311
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,375
Prince Luo's treason case.

312
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:14,000
What about it?

313
00:17:15,250 --> 00:17:16,208
You were ordered to kill

314
00:17:16,208 --> 00:17:19,125
Shen Lian, Qianhu
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau,

315
00:17:20,166 --> 00:17:22,583
and Xu Wenchang, Chief Secretary
of Prince Luo's household, and his wife.

316
00:17:23,541 --> 00:17:24,083
Who?

317
00:17:24,708 --> 00:17:25,958
Don't tell me you don't remember!

318
00:17:27,375 --> 00:17:28,791
I have killed countless people.

319
00:17:29,166 --> 00:17:31,250
I take the job. I never ask why.

320
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:34,958
As for this Shen Lian and Xu Wenchang,

321
00:17:35,958 --> 00:17:37,000
they mean nothing to me.

322
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:39,958
I want the truth.

323
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:50,708
How old are you?

324
00:17:52,875 --> 00:17:54,000
A few months younger

325
00:17:54,458 --> 00:17:55,583
than Xintian.

326
00:17:59,458 --> 00:18:00,166
Not right.

327
00:18:03,916 --> 00:18:04,625
Then back then,

328
00:18:05,375 --> 00:18:07,333
you were only eleven or twelve.

329
00:18:08,375 --> 00:18:09,791
You can't be the Leng Xin
from that case.

330
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:14,666
Can you die now?

331
00:18:18,875 --> 00:18:20,416
You still haven't answered my question.

332
00:18:23,208 --> 00:18:23,791
Fine.

333
00:18:24,458 --> 00:18:25,208
Ask something else.

334
00:18:26,375 --> 00:18:27,458
Something I know.

335
00:18:31,125 --> 00:18:31,625
Fine.

336
00:18:34,083 --> 00:18:35,750
Then what exactly is

337
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:36,750
the jade token used to command you?

338
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:55,690
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

339
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:59,440
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

340
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:02,690
♪My heart drifted lost♪

341
00:19:02,690 --> 00:19:06,100
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

342
00:19:07,190 --> 00:19:10,400
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

343
00:19:10,810 --> 00:19:14,150
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

344
00:19:14,730 --> 00:19:16,940
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

345
00:19:16,940 --> 00:19:20,980
♪I've softly let it go♪

346
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:24,850
♪The vow you made was true♪

347
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:28,600
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

348
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,810
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

349
00:19:30,810 --> 00:19:35,350
♪And forget at world's end♪

350
00:19:35,650 --> 00:19:37,150
♪Embracing memory♪

351
00:19:37,150 --> 00:19:39,520
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

352
00:19:39,520 --> 00:19:43,400
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

353
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,730
♪I wish to let it pass♪

354
00:19:45,730 --> 00:19:50,730
♪And run toward this vast life♪
